title: Vote for NFT.Farm Item Price Optimization
body:
The following governance vote is issued based on user request that abnormally low prices of items sold at NFT.Farm Shop negatively influence LOM Token economy. 

If we decide to raise the price, the number of tokens needed to purchase certain items will increase, but the overall value of the token left may quickly exceed the additional tokens you put down at current value. (70% of retrieved tokens will be burned and 25% will go to reward pool) 

Your options are:
1) keep the price of NFT.Farm Shop items 
2) raise the price of NFT.Farm Shop items purchasable with LOM Token 
3) raise the price of NFT.Farm Shop times purchasable with both LOM and ITAM Tokens 

Please note that only holders of ITAM, the governance token, will be able to participate in the vote. Make sure you have ITAM Token in your wallet at the snapshot point. For holders who are staking ITAM in certain pools, please reclaim your ITAM to take part. 

Thank you.
author: 0xe38526Dbe387FDaFaD76cAF9dEEAd525842a2a88
